Pepperoni Grill

Ingredients:
    [list]
    [*]Pepperoni x1
    [*]Salt 3g
    [*]Black Pepper 3g
    [*]Potato x1
    [*]Onion x1
    [/list]
Steps:
    Slice
        Pepperoni x1
        Potato x1
        Onion x1

    Season Pepperoni With
        Salt 3g
        Black Pepper 3g

    Grill
        Potato Slices x1
        Onion Slices x1
        Pepperoni Slice x2(Each Side)

    Transfer to Plate
        Pepperoni Slice x2
        Potato Slices x1
        Onion Slices x1

    Serve Hot